<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Index</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ECECE9;
            height: 60px;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .logo {
            margin-left: 30px;
            height: 60px;
        }

        .menu {
            margin-left: auto;
        }

        .lih {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .lih:hover {
            background-color: #1574D2;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        .container-custom {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            overflow: auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .color-rectangle {
            width: 100%; 
            height: 765px;
            background-color: #538AC6;
        }

        .image-container {
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center; 
            align-items: center; 
            height: 100%;
        }

        .centered-image {
            width: 100%; 
            height: auto;
            max-height: 100%;
        }

        .text-container {
            text-align: left;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 40px; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin-left: 50px; 
        }

        .bold-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 65px;
        }

        /* New container styles */
        .new-container {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: 260px; 
            background-color: #F5F7FA;
            margin: 0 auto;
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .new-container .inner-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .get-started-text {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 48px;
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .rectangle-button {
            width: 157px;
            height: 44px;
            background-color: #1574D2;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <partial name = "_NavBar" />

    <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="color-rectangle">
            <div class="image-container">
                <img src="~/images/handshake.jpg" alt="Centered Image" class="centered-image">
                <div class="text-container">
                    <p class="bold-text">You always deserve another chance</p>
                    <p>Embrace new beginnings and seize every opportunity. AnotherChance opens doors, connecting dreams with possibilities, and empowering individuals to rewrite their story.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="new-container">
            <div class="inner-content">
                <div class="get-started-text">GET STARTED HERE</div>
                <div class="quote-text">
                    Just because someone stumbles and loses their way, it doesnâ€™t mean they are lost forever<br>
                    - Professor X
                </div>
                <div class="rectangle-button">
                    <a asp-controller="AppUser" style="text-decoration: none; color: white" asp-action="CreateAppUser">GET STARTED</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
